               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                    (Book of Order of the Disciples, መጽሐፈ: ሥርዓቶሙ: ለሐዋርያት,) - this is the Apocryphal Acts of the Apostles
                    , arranged in eighteen sections: </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="154v" facs="001">Fols 1r–154v</locus>
                    <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1461Gadlah">Gadla ḥawāryāt
                                                  (general record)</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ: አብ: ወወልድ: ዝንቱ: መጽሐፈ: ሥርዓቶሙ ለሐዋርያት: ወባዕዳንሂ: እም: ፸ ወ ፱ አርድዕት:  ንኡሳን: ወዘኮነ: ኵሎ: እምዜናሆሙ:</incipit>
                    <note>Incomplete at the end</note>
